Dialogue: 99,0:00:02.23,0:00:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cranel!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:05.07,0:00:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem! Vamos ver como isso lida com isso!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:07.53,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fogo... {ED}
Dialogue: 99,0:00:08.32,0:00:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Não! Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...raio! {ED}
Dialogue: 99,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Que acabou de acontecer...? {ED}
Dialogue: 99,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Não é bom!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho que contra-atacar!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:46.73,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Saia daí! {ED}
Dialogue: 99,0:01:24.94,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bell!! {ED}
